	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.55]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Everyone has a different philosophy regarding rogues and AC.&nbsp;&nbsp;However,  I will agree that DEX is the single most important stat for a rogue. STR is next followed by AGI.  <br><br>I may just have to have my guild's master jeweler make me up those plat fire emerald rings.  And Ulthork Boots are still better than the banded I have now. Go for Iksar Hide gloves.  Good AC and nice STR and DEX buff.  I think VI had rogues in mind when they made those.<br><br>Thanks for the suggestions Daviv!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
